(5028, 185, 'content_block', 'While a monthly IT plan is great and ensures your business remains online, there are times when something else is needed. For example, you move offices or add a new location; You want to move all, or part, of your business to \"the Cloud\"; you want to completely overhaul the desktops in your office or change over from desktops to laptops or mobile devices. In those instances when special projects come up, ParksideTech can help.\r\n\r\nThere may even be times when you need another pair of eyes to look at a planned upgrade. You think you have a solid plan in place, but just want to make sure you\'ve covered all the bases. We\'re happy to sit down and discuss any and all of your options. We have years and years of experience in planning projects, both large and small; we\'ve purchased millions of dollars in hardware and software; we\'ve moved from 200 square feet of datacenter space and hundreds of server towers, to 10,000 square feet and hundreds of server racks. Let our experience help you make the best moves for your business.\r\n\r\nOur Consultation services include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Project Planning and Project Management</li>\r\n 	<li>vCIO - Virtual Chief Information Officer</li>\r\n 	<li>IT Strategy Planning</li>\r\n 	<li>Business Development and Operations Assistance</li>\r\n 	<li>VoIP System Planning and Implementation</li>\r\n 	<li>Hosted Service Provider Migrations</li>\r\n 	<li>Office Moves</li>\r\n 	<li>New Location Startups</li>\r\n 	<li>Datacenter Migrations</li>\r\n</ul>'),
