(5064, 51, 'content_block', 'Your business absolutely requires an online presence. That means MUCH more than simply having a website that lists some static details about what you do and where you are. These days, dynamic content is king. Your site should set you apart from your competitors and offer potential customers information about why you\'re the best at what you do.\r\n\r\nEven if you have a website now, how\'s it performing? Does it drive sales? Does it drive inquiries? Is it up-to-date or was is built in 2002 and hasn\'t changed much since it first went online? Do you even know how many people visit your site on a daily or monthly basis? ParksideTech can take a look at what you have and offer suggestions on how to improve on what you have: whether it\'s a full re-write or just building on what you have already.\r\n\r\nIn addition, there\'s social media. Do you have a Facebook page? What about a Twitter account? Instagram? Is your business using Google Local or Yelp? Should you be on one of these or ALL of them? We can help guide you to an effective social media strategy.\r\n\r\nAll of these items combine to form a coherent, efficient and profitable online presence. Our Online Presence solutions include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Website Design and Development - New Sites or Site Redesigns</li>\r\n 	<li>Content Management System Implementation</li>\r\n 	<li>Search Engine Optimization (SEO) Strategy</li>\r\n 	<li>Google Local/Business</li>\r\n 	<li>Social Media Strategy\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>LinkedIn</li>\r\n 	<li>Twitter</li>\r\n 	<li>Facebook</li>\r\n 	<li>Instagram</li>\r\n 	<li>Snapchat</li>\r\n 	<li>Yelp</li>\r\n 	<li>More</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>'),
